707970f-a.title: Manhattan: 2nd Avenue - 123rd Street (East)
707970f-a.text:
Second Ave., east side, north from and including East 123rd Street,
ahowing the Palace Theatre (motion pictures) bearing Nos. 2404-2408 and
a portion of the Second Ave. Elevated Line. Also seen (right) is No.
301-305 East 123rd Street, a 1-story brick house (covered with posters)
at the N.E. corner of Second Ave.
May 7, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
